Class ResultSubscription<R extends Result,P extends AsyncPagingIterable<Row,P>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.datastax.oss.dsbulk.executor.api.subscription.ResultSubscription<R,P>
  • Type Parameters:
    P - the page type, one of AsyncResultSet or ContinuousAsyncResultSet.
    R - the result type (WriteResult or ReadResult).
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Subscription
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ContinuousReadResultSubscription, ReadResultSubscription, WriteResultSubscription

    public abstract class ResultSubscription<R extends Result,P extends AsyncPagingIterable<Row,P>>
extends Object
implements Subscription
    A single-subscriber subscription that executes the provided Statement with the provided CqlSession and emits all the rows returned by the query to its Subscriber.
